            <title>How to Analyze Assets Based on Risk</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	In this 5-minute, 33-second video, Mike Poland of Life Cycle Engineering explains the analyze phase of a simple implementation model for a risk-based asset management system. Learn how to prioritize assets based on risk, map objects to failure and cause codes, and build master data with continuous improvement in mind.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
