            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:dd141956-e101-42c0-831b-9fde008d0288</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~3/SwIHZzK8rHI/case-ih-energy-certification</link>
