            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:df938575-24a5-4f3c-83f8-9e700087bf64</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~3/h6Gcp0luUDQ/ASQ-new-role-of-quality</link>
