            <title>Genentech Oceanside's continuous improvement journey</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	This video provides a talk with Kawa Chiu, associate director of manufacturing&amp;nbsp;at Genentech Oceanside,&amp;nbsp;about initial, and lasting, Right First Time successes.&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~4/_bbMZQpml4I" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2011-01-13T08:25:42-06:00</a10:updated>
            <a10:content type="text/html" src="http://reliableplant.com/View/28248/Genentech-continuous-improvement-journey" />
