            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~3/Su56LsR7pNo/Manufacturing-excellence-apprenticeships-KI</link>
            <a10:author>
                <a10:name>RP news wires</a10:name>
            </a10:author>
            <category>Videos</category>
            <category>Media Entries</category>
            <title>Manufacturing excellence and apprenticeships at KI</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Since the introduction of our first product in 1941, a steel folding chair, KI has recognized market needs and responded with welcome furniture solutions - products that skillfully support the success of customers in higher education, K-12, healthcare, business and government.&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
