            <title>Toyota plant in Alabama presents 'Quality Idol'</title>
            <description>&lt;p id="eow-description"&gt;
	Toyota Motor Manufacturing of Alabama brings you its first Quality Idol show.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~4/t4K_xH7a7uw" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-11-19T10:47:18-06:00</a10:updated>
