            <title>How to sustain improvement initiatives</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Mike Price, former chief executive of Ultraframe, speaks to Rebecca Piper from Cranfield School of Management about sustaining improvement initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~4/sd5hJyxJk8o" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
