            <title>Tom Peters on the importance of unsexy solutions</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	This video is a&amp;nbsp;reminder from Tom Peters that unsexy solutions can be tremendously valuable, on the scale of tens of thousands of lives saved.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/continuous_improvement/~4/Qdoi5lJ3oLI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-09-28T09:09:18-05:00</a10:updated>
